# tf.contrib.graph_editor.swap_ios

``` python
tf.contrib.graph_editor.swap_ios(
    sgv0,
    sgv1
)
```

Defined in [`tensorflow/contrib/graph_editor/reroute.py`](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.13/tensorflow/contrib/graph_editor/reroute.py).
